        "full_html": "<h4 style='color: var(--accent-blue); margin: 1.5rem 0 0.5rem;'>■ 本日の要点</h4>\n<ul style='padding-left: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.6;'>\n<li style='margin-bottom: 0.3rem;'>更新あり**: Artemis II (SLS) 打ち上げまであと1週間。機体はパッド39Bにあり、最終準備中。</li>\n<li style='margin-bottom: 0.3rem;'>更新あり<strong style='color: #fff;'>: </strong>本日(3/25)**、Rocket Lab Electron \"Daughter of the Stars\" がNZから打ち上げ予定。</li>\n<li style='margin-bottom: 0.3rem;'>更新あり**: 昨日(3/24)、SpaceX Falcon 9 (Starlink) は無事に打ち上げ成功。</li>\n<li style='margin-bottom: 0.3rem;'>新規**: 3/29に SpaceX Transporter 16 (Rideshare) の打ち上げが控えています。</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 style='color: var(--accent-blue); margin: 1.5rem 0 0.5rem;'>■ 打ち上げ一覧</h4>\n<div style='overflow-x: auto; margin: 1rem 0;'><table style='width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-secondary);'>\n<tr><th style='border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); padding: 0.6rem; text-align: left; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); color: #fff;'></th><th style='border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); padding: 0.6rem; text-align: left; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); color: #fff;'>打ち上げ日</th><th style='border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); padding: 0.6rem; text-align: left; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); color: #fff;'>ロケット</th><th style='border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); padding: 0.6rem; text-align: left; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); color: #fff;'>ミッション</th><th style='border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); padding: 0.6rem; text-align: left; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); color: #fff;'>発射場</th><th style='border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); padding: 0.6rem; text-align: left; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); color: #fff;'>見学</th><th style='border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); padding: 0.6rem; text-align: left; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); color: #fff;'>公式</th><th style='border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); padding: 0.6rem; text-align: left